Description: Import and handling data from vegetation-plot databases,
        especially data stored in 'Turboveg 2'
        (<https://www.synbiosys.alterra.nl/turboveg/>). Also
        import/export routines for exchange of data with 'Juice'
        (<https://www.sci.muni.cz/botany/juice/>) are implemented.
